                        <interp inst="t18741026-name-167" type="given" value="DANIEL"></interp>DANIEL BELL</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">re-called</hi>). A transfer for 500Z. is missing, but that is a thing that could easily be made-good.</p>
